description: Stream Live IPTV, Video On-Demand, and Series from an Xtream-compatible server using this plugin.
name: Jellyfin Xtream
overview: Stream content from an Xtream-compatible server.

versions.changelog: Introduce native Live TV restream capabilities. This enables sharing a single Xtream Live TV stream with multiple clients and thus using less concurrent active streams from the Xtream provider.
Make the plugin compatible with Jellyfin v10.8.0 release.
Introduce native Live TV integration (#3) with the ability to select which channels are included and EPG support.
Initial release of the Jellyfin.Xtream plugin.
